Method Detail

getTaskId

long getTaskId()
The source task ID of this result, can be used to track the task that produced this result.

getResult

TResult getResult()
The result of a function. Actions do not change this field (i.e. it holds the default(TResult) value). If an exception has occurred then accessing this property throws the exception.

Throws:
TaskResultException - May throw an exception, if the task that created this result caused an exception instead of creating an actual result.

getError

java.lang.Throwable getError()
If an exception occurs during a task, it is stored here. If no exceptions occurred, this is null.

isSuccessful

boolean isSuccessful()
Returns true if no exceptions occurred, i.e. the task was successfully completed.
